responseText: The Obsidian Jackals are all over that wreck over there, no doubt looking for plunder overlooked by previous looters. They don't know the history that they tread upon, though, not like we do. The Zephyr Wind are the rightful keepers of that history. Don't you think?
name: EVT_SAN_0012_JadeScorpion_ZephyrWind_Turnin_DLG_5_Response
